snippet.title: Sprint Master for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
A REALLY good game for your Atari 2600. :)

This racing game offers many tracks, all with 3 variations (blacktop, dirt and ice)

Yeah, I used the easiest track, as I'm not that good on the harder ones. =(
